{"tid":860242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一post支持大家聽日行出黎","createTime":"2018-10-13T07:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T10:22:57.000Z","uid":153689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d5720103a638ac0ac37b8722d08b808685e36b01","tid":860242,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T07:51:27.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔知到時會有幾多人<br />\n即使唔合理我都會同自己講：<br />\n<br />\n我去，大家都會去<br />\n<br />\n就算留言幾多負面言論我都唔會理<br />\n因為喱次阻唔到，香港就乜柒都無。<br />\n<br />\n你未來至少14年既社會福利都會受影響<br />\n所以唔好再覺得同你無關<br />\n<br />\n你唔爭取，第時比大陸狗笑騎騎袋你辛苦賺既錢交既稅，你甘心咩？<br />\n<br />\n你甘心未來交比政府既錢，都繼續斷送比無貢獻無付出既大陸狗咩？<br />\n<br />\n你甘心咩？<br />\n<br />\n10月14日 銅鑼灣東角道 3點為香港剩低既少少希望掙扎<br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫手一人一post<br />\n<br />\n轉自<a href=\"https://lih.kg/859672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/859672</a>"},{"pid":"9eede76f7490fde38fef89efa3afec672ed269fd","tid":860242,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T08:41:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb7d37a18e7222f48fd819a45be1f92b15c410d2","tid":860242,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T08:45:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0d1063e8f7d195bfde53a06cf8cae64d083d661","tid":860242,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T10:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}